plymouth for Debian
-------------------

The following steps are required in order to enable the plymouth bootsplash:

  * Install plymouth and one or more of the plugin packages.
  * Add 'splash' as boot parameter in your bootloader configuration.
  * Configure the default plugin by running plymouth-set-default-theme.

